snippet.title: Num One: Revised Edition Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
The unique mathematical match-3 game Num One is coming back! Ported from mobile to PC for release on Steam!

Num One: Revised Edition is a mathematical twist on a match-3 puzzle game. Combine and level up numbers, allowing them to swap further distances. 1s make 3s, 3s, make 9s, 9s make 27s, etc. Can you make a 2187?

Wishlist today on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1871880/Num_One_Revised_Edition/

Stock media (Ambient House (Chill Background Music)) provided by EMilar / Pond5
